{
  "stem": "18102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 126.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know of any other Polish cities were allowed to have full-time parochial schools, meaning in Yiddish where the full curriculum was in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you graduated from there to go on to gymnasium, which is high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a Polish high school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was accredited grammar schools from which you could go to high school, and then later if you could get to university.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, Jews didn't get to university very often.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the schools were accredited, and therefore needed qualified teachers to be accredited.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother, for instance, had become a teacher in the Vilna teacher's seminar, which was very famous throughout Poland as a very high level of school of education for teachers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- he went to-- I think it was a Belgian school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I forgot the name right here now of where he graduated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But at any rate, my mother went to Vilna seminar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father must have attended classes there as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Although, he wasn't a full-time student.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I never saw his graduation papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I saw hers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother was a straight-A student.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she a couple of times showed me her graduation and her marks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But my father met my mother at the Vilna seminar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I know that he must have attended some classes there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At any rate, they were very qualified teachers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my mother taught the younger-- now, in-- in that day when you taught a class, you taught them everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There wasn't any you-- you went to a science teacher for science or a math teacher for math.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The grade school teacher was your teacher in every subject.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
